-- Hockey Says Coalition Will Rescind Australia Mining Tax as Bad for Jobs
-- Marion Rae
-- 2010-07-01T21:26:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/hockey-says-coalition-will-rescind-australia-mining-tax-as-bad-for-jobs.html

          
          
             The mining tax is a bad tax with
negative implications for investment in Australia and will be
rescinded by the Liberal-National coalition, opposition finance
spokesman Joe Hockey told Australian Broadcasting Corp. radio
today.  
